                <sampler disabled="true" name="Log Monitor CARE ORDERS">
                    <plugin>
                        <fkm>
                            <display>
                                <columns>
                                    <column>filename</column>
                                    <column>permissions</column>
                                    <column>status</column>
                                    <column>triggerCount</column>
                                    <column>triggerDetails</column>
                                    <column>secondsSinceLastTrigger</column>
                                    <column>updateRate</column>
                                    <column>lastModificationTime</column>
                                    <column>secondsSinceLastModified</column>
                                    <column>fileSize</column>
                                    <column>absolutePath</column>
                                </columns>
                                <triggerMode>MULTIPLE</triggerMode>
                                <triggerCountMode>SUM</triggerCountMode>
                            </display>
                            <files>
                                <file>
                                    <source>
                                        <filename>
                                            <var ref="FIXLOG"></var>
                                        </filename>
                                    </source>
                                    <tables>
                                        <table>
                                            <severity>warning</severity>
                                            <keyTable>
                                                <data>
                                                    <keys>
                                                        <key>
                                                            <setKey>
                                                                <match>
                                                                    <searchString>
                                                                        <data>\[ INPUT raw MSG    \].*35=D.*21=3</data>
                                                                    </searchString>
                                                                    <rules>REGEXP</rules>
                                                                </match>
                                                            </setKey>
                                                        </key>
                                                    </keys>
                                                </data>
                                            </keyTable>
                                        </table>
                                    </tables>
                                    <alias>
                                        <data>CARE ORDER</data>
                                    </alias>
                                </file>
                            </files>
                        </fkm>
                    </plugin>
                </sampler>

                    <plugin>
                        <fkm>
                            <display>
                                <columns>
                                    <column>filename</column>
                                    <column>permissions</column>
                                    <column>status</column>
                                    <column>triggerCount</column>

                    <plugin>
                        <sql-toolkit>
                            <queries>
                                <query>
                                    <name>
                                        <data>ShowTables</data>
                                    </name>
                                    <sql>
                                        <data>show table status</data>
                                    </sql>
                                </query>
                                <query>
                                    <name>
                                        <data>DMA Slow Orders</data>
                                    </name>
                                    <sql>
                                        <data>SELECT id.VALUE ID, a.VALUE Category, FROM_UNIXTIME( st.TIME_SEEN, &apos;%e-%b-%Y %H:%i:%S&apos; ) SEEN, ( ft.TIME_SEEN - st.TIME_SEEN ) LATENCY FROM lat_time st INNER JOIN lat_time ft ON ft.ID = st.ID AND ft.NAME = &apos;DMA Ack&apos; INNER JOIN lat_id id ON id.ID = st.ID AND id.NAME = &apos;Id&apos; INNER JOIN lat_attrib a ON a.ID=st.ID and a.NAME=&apos;SecurityExchange&apos; WHERE (st.NAME = &apos;DMA NewOrder&apos; OR st.NAME = &apos;DMA CancelReplace&apos;) AND ( ft.TIME_SEEN - st.TIME_SEEN ) &gt; 0.15   ORDER BY st.TIME_SEEN</data>
                                    </sql>
                                </query>
                                <query>
                                    <name>
                                        <data>CARE Slow Orders</data>
                                    </name>
                                    <sql>
                                        <data>SELECT id.VALUE ID, a.VALUE Category, FROM_UNIXTIME( st.TIME_SEEN, &apos;%e-%b-%Y %H:%i:%S&apos; ) SEEN, ( ft.TIME_SEEN - st.TIME_SEEN ) LATENCY FROM lat_time st INNER JOIN lat_time ft ON ft.ID = st.ID AND ft.NAME = &apos;CARE Ack&apos; INNER JOIN lat_id id ON id.ID = st.ID AND id.NAME = &apos;Id&apos; INNER JOIN lat_attrib a ON a.ID=st.ID and a.NAME=&apos;SecurityExchange&apos; WHERE (st.NAME = &apos;CARE NewOrder&apos; OR st.NAME = &apos;CARE CancelReplace&apos;) AND ( ft.TIME_SEEN - st.TIME_SEEN ) &gt; 300.0 ORDER BY st.TIME_SEEN</data>
                                    </sql>
                                </query>
                                <query>
                                    <name>
                                        <data>All Cancel Rejects</data>
                                    </name>
                                    <sql>
                                        <data>SELECT id.VALUE ID, a.VALUE Category, FROM_UNIXTIME( st.TIME_SEEN, &apos;%e-%b-%Y %H:%i:%S&apos; ) SEEN, ( ft.TIME_SEEN - st.TIME_SEEN ) LATENCY FROM lat_time st INNER JOIN lat_time ft ON ft.ID = st.ID AND ft.NAME = &apos;CARE Ack&apos; INNER JOIN lat_id id ON id.ID = st.ID AND id.NAME = &apos;Id&apos; INNER JOIN lat_attrib a ON a.ID=st.ID and a.NAME=&apos;SecurityExchange&apos; WHERE (st.NAME = &apos;CancelRequest&apos;) AND ( ft.TIME_SEEN - st.TIME_SEEN ) &gt; 300.0 ORDER BY st.TIME_SEEN</data>
                                    </sql>
                                </query>
                            </queries>

                <sampler name="SQL">
                    <sampleInterval>
                        <data>60</data>
                    </sampleInterval>
                    <plugin>
                        <sql-toolkit>
                            <queries>
                                <query>
                                    <name>
                                        <data>ShowTables</data>
                                    </name>
                                    <sql>
                                        <data>show table status</data>
                                    </sql>
                                </query>
                                <query>
                                    <name>
                                        <data>DMA Slow Orders</data>
                                    </name>
                                    <sql>
                                        <data>SELECT id.VALUE ID, a.VALUE Category, FROM_UNIXTIME( st.TIME_SEEN, &apos;%e-%b-%Y %H:%i:%S&apos; ) SEEN, ( ft.TIME_SEEN - st.TIME_SEEN ) LATENCY FROM lat_time st INNER JOIN lat_time ft ON ft.ID = st.ID AND ft.NAME = &apos;DMA Ack&apos; INNER JOIN lat_id id ON id.ID = st.ID AND id.NAME = &apos;Id&apos; INNER JOIN lat_attrib a ON a.ID=st.ID and a.NAME=&apos;SecurityExchange&apos; WHERE (st.NAME = &apos;DMA NewOrder&apos; OR st.NAME = &apos;DMA CancelReplace&apos;) AND ( ft.TIME_SEEN - st.TIME_SEEN ) &gt; 0.15   ORDER BY st.TIME_SEEN</data>
                                    </sql>
                                </query>
                                <query>
                                    <name>
                                        <data>CARE Slow Orders</data>
                                    </name>
                                    <sql>
                                        <data>SELECT id.VALUE ID, a.VALUE Category, FROM_UNIXTIME( st.TIME_SEEN, &apos;%e-%b-%Y %H:%i:%S&apos; ) SEEN, ( ft.TIME_SEEN - st.TIME_SEEN ) LATENCY FROM lat_time st INNER JOIN lat_time ft ON ft.ID = st.ID AND ft.NAME = &apos;CARE Ack&apos; INNER JOIN lat_id id ON id.ID = st.ID AND id.NAME = &apos;Id&apos; INNER JOIN lat_attrib a ON a.ID=st.ID and a.NAME=&apos;SecurityExchange&apos; WHERE (st.NAME = &apos;CARE NewOrder&apos; OR st.NAME = &apos;CARE CancelReplace&apos;) AND ( ft.TIME_SEEN - st.TIME_SEEN ) &gt; 300.0 ORDER BY st.TIME_SEEN</data>
                                    </sql>
                                </query>
                                <query>
                                    <name>
                                        <data>All Cancel Rejects</data>
                                    </name>
                                    <sql>
                                        <data>SELECT id.VALUE ID, a.VALUE Category, FROM_UNIXTIME( st.TIME_SEEN, &apos;%e-%b-%Y %H:%i:%S&apos; ) SEEN, ( ft.TIME_SEEN - st.TIME_SEEN ) LATENCY FROM lat_time st INNER JOIN lat_time ft ON ft.ID = st.ID AND ft.NAME = &apos;CARE Ack&apos; INNER JOIN lat_id id ON id.ID = st.ID AND id.NAME = &apos;Id&apos; INNER JOIN lat_attrib a ON a.ID=st.ID and a.NAME=&apos;SecurityExchange&apos; WHERE (st.NAME = &apos;CancelRequest&apos;) AND ( ft.TIME_SEEN - st.TIME_SEEN ) &gt; 300.0 ORDER BY st.TIME_SEEN</data>
                                    </sql>
                                </query>
                            </queries>
                            <connection>
                                <database>
                                    <mysql>
                                        <serverName>elonxaphubp3.uk.ml.com</serverName>
                                        <databaseName>rogerstest_louat</databaseName>
                                        <port>3306</port>

            <samplerGroup name="Missing Execs">
                <samplerGroup name="Missing Executions">
                    <sampler name="INPUT">
                        <sampleInterval>
                            <data>10</data>
                        </sampleInterval>
                        <plugin>
                            <message-tracker>
                                <adapters>
                                    <adapter name="InputLog">
                                        <checkpoint>
                                            <data>INPUT</data>
                                        </checkpoint>
                                        <source>
                                            <file>
                                                <filename>
                                                    <data>/var/tmp/fileA</data>
                                                </filename>
                                            </file>
                                        </source>
                                        <formatType>
                                            <data>
                                                <regex>
                                                    <tags>
                                                        <tag name="EXCH">
                                                            <data>
                                                                <regex>10005=(.+?)\001</regex>
                                                            </data>
                                                        </tag>
                                                        <tag name="EXCH_TRD_CODE">
                                                            <data>
                                                                <regex>10006=.+EXCH_TRD_CODE=(.+?)\|</regex>
                                                            </data>
                                                        </tag>
                                                        <tag name="TAG55">
                                                            <data>
                                                                <regex>55=(.+?)\001</regex>
                                                            </data>
                                                        </tag>
                                                        <tag name="TAG32">
                                                            <data>
                                                                <regex>32=(.+?)\001</regex>
                                                            </data>
                                                        </tag>
                                                        <tag name="TAG31">
                                                            <data>
                                                                <regex>31=(.+?)\001</regex>
                                                            </data>
                                                        </tag>
                                                        <tag name="TAG207">
                                                            <data>
                                                                <regex>207=(.+?)\001</regex>
                                                            </data>
                                                        </tag>

   cp rowNames.`date +%y%m%d`.txt rowNames.txt

        <rule name=" POUYA2_Andras">
            <targets>
                <target></target>
            </targets>
            <priority>1</priority>
            <block>
                <if>
                    <equal>
                        <dataItem>
                            <property>@value</property>
                        </dataItem>
                        <string>COMPLETED</string>
                    </equal>
                    <transaction>
                        <update>
                            <property>state/@severity</property>

                        <property>@value</property>

                            <var ref="today"></var>
                            <var ref="yesterday"></var>
                        </subtract>
                    </abs>

                <set>
                    <var ref="percentagediff"></var>
                    <multiply>

                            <var ref="diff"></var>
                            <var ref="today"></var>
                        </divide>
                        <integer>100</integer>
                    </multiply>
                </set>
                <if>
                    <gt>
                        <var ref="percentagediff"></var>
                        <integer>10</integer>

                            <property>state/@severity</property>
                            <severity>warning</severity>
                        </update>
                    </transaction>

                            <property>state/@severity</property>

            </targets>

                <pathAlias name="ExDt">../cell[(@column=&quot;value&quot;)]</pathAlias>
            </pathAliases>

                    <dataItem>
                        <pathAlias ref="ExDt"></pathAlias>
                        <property>@value</property>
                    </dataItem>
                </set>
                <set>
                    <var ref="X"></var>
                    <parseDate>
                        <string>%d %B %Y</string>
                        <dataItem>
                            <pathAlias ref="ExDt"></pathAlias>
                            <property>@value</property>
                        </dataItem>
                    </parseDate>
                </set>
                <set>
                    <var ref="days"></var>
                    <format>
                        <string>%d</string>
                        <divide>
                            <subtract>
                                <parseDate>
                                    <string>%d %B %Y</string>
                                    <dataItem>
                                        <pathAlias ref="ExDt"></pathAlias>
                                        <property>@value</property>
                                    </dataItem>
                                </parseDate>
                                <now></now>
                            </subtract>
                            <integer>86400</integer>
                        </divide>
                    </format>
                </set>
                <if>
                    <lt>
                        <var ref="days"></var>
                        <integer>0</integer>
                    </lt>
                    <transaction>
                        <update>
                            <property>state/@severity</property>
                            <severity>critical</severity>
                        </update>
                        <update>
                            <property>@value</property>
                            <string>Expired</string>
                        </update>
                    </transaction>
                    <if>
                        <and>
                            <gte>
                                <var ref="days"></var>
                                <integer>0</integer>
                            </gte>
                            <lte>
                                <var ref="days"></var>
                                <integer>4</integer>
                            </lte>
                        </and>
                        <transaction>
                            <update>
                                <property>state/@severity</property>
                                <severity>critical</severity>
                            </update>
                            <update>
                                <property>@value</property>
                                <var ref="days"></var>
                            </update>
                        </transaction>
                        <if>
                            <and>
                                <gte>
                                    <var ref="days"></var>
                                    <integer>5</integer>
                                </gte>
                                <lte>
                                    <var ref="days"></var>
                                    <integer>10</integer>
                                </lte>
                            </and>
                            <transaction>
                                <update>
                                    <property>state/@severity</property>
                                    <severity>warning</severity>
                                </update>
                                <update>
                                    <property>@value</property>
                                    <var ref="days"></var>
                                </update>
                            </transaction>
                            <transaction>
                                <update>
                                    <property>state/@severity</property>
                                    <severity>ok</severity>
                                </update>
                                <update>
                                    <property>@value</property>
                                    <var ref="days"></var>
                                </update>
                            </transaction>
                        </if>
                    </if>
                </if>
            </block>

        <rule name="Computed Rule - format to 2 places duration weighted avg for 10 min period">
            <targets>
                <target>/geneos/gateway/directory/probe/managedEntity/sampler[(@name=&quot;Computed&quot;)][(@type=&quot;&quot;)]/dataview[(@name=&quot;Computed&quot;)]/rows/row/cell[(@column=&quot;Percentage time above 8%&quot;)]</target>
            </targets>
            <priority>1</priority>
            <pathAliases>
                <pathAlias name="Above Threshold">../cell[(@column=&quot;1WhenAboveThreshold&quot;)]</pathAlias>
                <pathAlias name="Original value">../cell[(@column=&quot;percentUtilisation&quot;)]</pathAlias>
                <pathAlias name="NT value">../cell[(@column=&quot;%processorTime&quot;)]</pathAlias>
            </pathAliases>
            <block>
                <!--if path "Original value" value > 8 then-->
                <!--  value format("%.2f %%", durationWeightedAverage(path "Above Threshold" value for "1mins") * 100)-->
                <!--else if path "Original value" value <= 8 then-->
                <!--  value format("%.2f %%", durationWeightedAverage(path "Above Threshold" value for "1mins") * 100)-->
                <!--endif-->
                <!--if path "Original value" value > 8 then-->
                <if>
                    <gt>
                        <dataItem>
                            <pathAlias ref="NT value"></pathAlias>
                            <property>@value</property>
                        </dataItem>
                        <integer>18</integer>
                    </gt>
                    <transaction>
                        <update>
                            <property>@value</property>
                            <format>
                                <string>%.2f %%</string>
                                <multiply>
                                    <durationWeightedAverage>
                                        <historicalDataItem>
                                            <pathAlias ref="Above Threshold"></pathAlias>
                                            <property>@value</property>
                                            <historyPeriod ref="10mins"></historyPeriod>
                                        </historicalDataItem>
                                    </durationWeightedAverage>
                                    <integer>100</integer>
                                </multiply>

            <!--Context set to consider snooze state of all levels above cell.-->
            <targets>
                <target>//cell</target>
            </targets>
            <priority>1</priority>
            <block>
                <set>
                    <var ref="parents"></var>
                    <maximum>
                        <dataItem>
                            <property>state/@snoozedParents</property>
                        </dataItem>
                    </maximum>
                </set>
                <set>
                    <var ref="A"></var>
                    <string>YIPPEE</string>
                </set>
                <!--if maximum(wpath "Status1" severity) = critical then-->
                <!--  severity warning-->
                <!--  value "Down"-->
                <!--else-->
                <!--  severity ok-->
                <!--  value "Up"-->
                <!--endif-->

        <rule name="Percent RAM used">
            <targets>
                <target>/geneos/gateway/directory/probe/managedEntity/sampler/dataview[(@name=&quot;hardware&quot;)]/rows/row[(@name=&quot;PercentRAMused&quot;)]/cell[(@column=&quot;Value&quot;)]</target>
            </targets>
            <priority>1</priority>
            <pathAliases>
                <pathAlias name="TotalMem">../../row[(@name=&quot;totalPhysicalMemory&quot;)]/cell[(@column=&quot;Value&quot;)]</pathAlias>
                <pathAlias name="UsedMem">../../row[(@name=&quot;memoryUse&quot;)]/cell[(@column=&quot;Value&quot;)]</pathAlias>
            </pathAliases>
            <block>
                <transaction>
                    <update>
                        <property>@value</property>
                        <format>
                            <string>5.0f %%</string>
                            <multiply>
                                <divide>
                                    <dataItem>
                                        <pathAlias ref="UsedMem"></pathAlias>
                                        <property>@value</property>
                                    </dataItem>
                                    <dataItem>
                                        <pathAlias ref="TotalMem"></pathAlias>
                                        <property>@value</property>
                                    </dataItem>
                                </divide>
                                <integer>100</integer>
                            </multiply>
                        </format>
                    </update>
                </transaction>
            </block>
        </rule>
        <rule disabled="true" name="Ping rounded up">
            <targets>
                <target>/geneos/gateway/directory/probe/managedEntity/sampler[(@name=&quot;ping&quot;)][(@type=&quot;&quot;)]/dataview[(@name=&quot;ping&quot;)]/rows/row/cell[(@column=&quot;rounded&quot;)]</target>
            </targets>
            <priority>1</priority>
            <pathAliases>
                <pathAlias name="val">../cell[(@column=&quot;RoundtripTime&quot;)]</pathAlias>
            </pathAliases>
            <evaluateOnDataviewSample>true</evaluateOnDataviewSample>
            <block>
                <!--value format("%d", value + 0.51)-->
                <set>
                    <var ref="X"></var>
                    <dataItem>
                        <pathAlias ref="val"></pathAlias>
                        <property>@value</property>
                    </dataItem>
                </set>
                <transaction>
                    <update>
                        <property>@value</property>
                        <format>
                            <string>%d</string>
                            <add>
                                <var ref="X"></var>
                                <double>0.99</double>
                            </add>
                        </format>
                    </update>
                </transaction>
            </block>
        </rule>

        <rule name="ruleEmmaOnTheWireNetprobeMandatoryProccess">

            </targets>
            <priority>1</priority>
            <block>
                <if>
                    <equal>
                        <dataItem>
                            <property>@value</property>
                        </dataItem>
                        <integer>0</integer>
                    </equal>

                        <update>
                            <property>state/@severity</property>
                            <severity>critical</severity>
                        </update>
                    </transaction>

                        <update>
                            <property>state/@severity</property>
                            <severity>ok</severity>
                        </update>
                    </transaction>
                </if>
                <if>
                    <and>
                        <notEqual>
                            <dataItem>
                                <property>state/@severity</property>
                            </dataItem>
                            <dataItem>
                                <property>state/@severity</property>
                                <previous>true</previous>
                            </dataItem>
                        </notEqual>
                        <equal>
                            <dataItem>
                                <property>state/@severity</property>
                            </dataItem>
                            <severity>critical</severity>
                        </equal>
                    </and>
                    <transaction>
                        <userData>
                            <name>_MYSUBJECT</name>
                            <value>
                                <data>$_SEVERITY $_GATEWAY - (live) Geneos process missing ($_processName)</data>
                            </value>
                        </userData>
                        <userData>

                            <value>

                            </value>
                        </userData>
                        <userData>
                            <name>_ALWAYSDUMP</name>
                            <value>
                                <data>set</data>
                            </value>
                        </userData>
                        <userData>
                            <name>_MYBODY</name>
                            <value>
                                <data>The mandatory (live) Geneos process &quot;$_processName&quot; is missing\nDetected by ruleHorizonNetprobeMandatoryProccess</data>
                            </value>
                        </userData>
                        <action ref="actionAlertSupport"></action>
                    </transaction>
                    <if>
                        <and>
                            <and>
                                <notEqual>
                                    <dataItem>
                                        <property>state/@severity</property>
                                        <previous>true</previous>
                                    </dataItem>
                                    <severity>undefined</severity>
                                </notEqual>
                                <notEqual>
                                    <dataItem>
                                        <property>state/@severity</property>
                                    </dataItem>
                                    <dataItem>
                                        <property>state/@severity</property>
                                        <previous>true</previous>
                                    </dataItem>
                                </notEqual>
                            </and>
                            <equal>
                                <dataItem>
                                    <property>state/@severity</property>
                                </dataItem>

                            </equal>
                        </and>

                            <userData>

            <pathAliases>

            </pathAliases>
            <evaluateOnDataviewSample>true</evaluateOnDataviewSample>
            <block>
                <set>
                    <var ref="minutes"></var>
                    <format>
                        <string>%d</string>
                        <divide>
                            <dataItem>
                                <pathAlias ref="seconds"></pathAlias>
                                <property>@value</property>
                            </dataItem>
                            <integer>60</integer>
                        </divide>
                    </format>
                </set>
                <set>
                    <var ref="Pseconds"></var>
                    <subtract>
                        <dataItem>
                            <pathAlias ref="seconds"></pathAlias>
                            <property>@value</property>
                        </dataItem>
                        <multiply>
                            <var ref="minutes"></var>
                            <integer>60</integer>
                        </multiply>
                    </subtract>
                </set>
                <set>
                    <var ref="hours"></var>
                    <format>
                        <string>%d</string>
                        <divide>
                            <var ref="minutes"></var>
                            <integer>60</integer>
                        </divide>
                    </format>
                </set>
                <set>
                    <var ref="Pminutes"></var>
                    <subtract>
                        <var ref="minutes"></var>
                        <multiply>
                            <var ref="hours"></var>
                            <integer>60</integer>
                        </multiply>
                    </subtract>
                </set>
                <set>
                    <var ref="days"></var>
                    <format>
                        <string>%d</string>
                        <divide>
                            <var ref="hours"></var>
                            <integer>24</integer>
                        </divide>
                    </format>
                </set>
                <set>
                    <var ref="Phours"></var>
                    <subtract>
                        <var ref="hours"></var>
                        <multiply>
                            <var ref="days"></var>
                            <integer>24</integer>
                        </multiply>
                    </subtract>
                </set>
                <transaction>
                    <update>
                        <property>@value</property>
                        <concat>
                            <var ref="days"></var>
                            <string> Days </string>
                            <var ref="Phours"></var>
                            <string> Hours </string>
                            <var ref="Pminutes"></var>
                            <string> Minutes </string>
                            <var ref="Pseconds"></var>
                            <string> Seconds </string>
                        </concat>
                    </update>
                </transaction>
            </block>

                <pathAlias name="gateway_ME">/geneos/gateway[(@name=var(&quot;gateway&quot;))]/directory/probe/managedEntity/sampler[wild(@name,&quot;Autosnooze*&quot;)][(@type=&quot;&quot;)]/dataview[wild(@name,&quot;Autosnooze*&quot;)]/rows/row/cell[(@value=var(&quot;rowName&quot;))][(@column=&quot;Target&quot;)]/../cell[(@column=&quot;Gateway&quot;)]</pathAlias>
                <pathAlias name="netprobe_ME">/geneos/gateway[(@name=var(&quot;gateway&quot;))]/directory/probe/managedEntity/sampler[wild(@name,&quot;Autosnooze*&quot;)][(@type=&quot;&quot;)]/dataview[wild(@name,&quot;Autosnooze*&quot;)]/rows/row/cell[(@value=var(&quot;rowName&quot;))][(@column=&quot;Target&quot;)]/../cell[(@column=&quot;Target&quot;)]</pathAlias>
            </pathAliases>
            <block>
                <if>
                    <and>
                        <and>
                            <equal>
                                <target>
                                    <netprobeName></netprobeName>
                                </target>
                                <first>
                                    <dataItems>
                                        <pathAlias ref="netprobe_ME"></pathAlias>
                                        <property>@value</property>
                                    </dataItems>
                                </first>
                            </equal>
                            <like>
                                <dataItem>
                                    <pathAlias ref="snoozed_ME"></pathAlias>
                                    <property>@value</property>
                                </dataItem>
                                <string>snooze</string>
                            </like>
                        </and>
                        <equal>
                            <first>
                                <dataItems>
                                    <pathAlias ref="gateway_ME"></pathAlias>
                                    <property>@value</property>
                                </dataItems>
                            </first>
                            <target>
                                <gatewayName></gatewayName>
                            </target>
                        </equal>
                    </and>
                    <transaction>
                        <action ref="to snooze ME2"></action>
                    </transaction>
                    <if>
                        <and>
                            <and>
                                <equal>
                                    <target>
                                        <netprobeName></netprobeName>
                                    </target>
                                    <first>
                                        <dataItems>
                                            <pathAlias ref="netprobe_ME"></pathAlias>
                                            <property>@value</property>
                                        </dataItems>
                                    </first>
                                </equal>
                                <like>
                                    <dataItem>
                                        <pathAlias ref="snoozed_ME"></pathAlias>
                                        <property>@value</property>
                                    </dataItem>
                                    <string>unsnooze</string>
                                </like>
                            </and>
                            <equal>
                                <first>
                                    <dataItems>
                                        <pathAlias ref="gateway_ME"></pathAlias>
                                        <property>@value</property>
                                    </dataItems>
                                </first>
                                <target>
                                    <gatewayName></gatewayName>
                                </target>
                            </equal>

                            <action ref="to unsnooze ME2"></action>
                        </transaction>
                    </if>

            <rule name="ITRSChk_Frequency">
                <targets>
                    <target>/geneos/gateway/directory/probe/managedEntity/sampler[wild(@name,&quot;ITRSChk*&quot;)][(@type=&quot;&quot;)]/dataview/rows/row/cell[(@column=&quot;Frequency&quot;)]</target>
                </targets>
                <priority>1</priority>
                <pathAliases>
                    <pathAlias name="FeedName">../cell[(@column=&quot;FeedName&quot;)]</pathAlias>
                </pathAliases>
                <block>
                    <set>
                        <var ref="X"></var>
                        <dataItem>
                            <pathAlias ref="FeedName"></pathAlias>
                            <property>@value</property>
                        </dataItem>
                    </set>
                    <if>
                        <like>
                            <var ref="X"></var>
                            <string></string>
                        </like>
                        <transaction>
                            <update>
                                <property>@value</property>
                                <string></string>
                            </update>
                        </transaction>
                        <if>
                            <inList>
                                <var ref="X"></var>
                                <string>Bloomberg</string>
                                <string>Ramp</string>
                            </inList>
                            <transaction>
                                <update>
                                    <property>@value</property>
                                    <string>Daily</string>
                                </update>
                            </transaction>
                            <if>
                                <inList>
                                    <var ref="X"></var>
                                    <string>Other</string>
                                    <string>FRG</string>
                                </inList>
                                <transaction>
                                    <update>
                                        <property>@value</property>
                                        <string>Weekly</string>
                                    </update>
                                </transaction>
                                <transaction>
                                    <update>
                                        <property>@value</property>
                                        <string>Monthly</string>
                                    </update>
                                </transaction>
                            </if>
                        </if>
                    </if>
                </block>
            </rule>
            <rule name="ITRSChk_Frequency2">
                <targets>
                    <target>/geneos/gateway/directory/probe/managedEntity/sampler/dataview[(@name=&quot;ITRSChk_Combination&quot;)]/rows/row/cell[(@column=&quot;TimeSinceLastUpdate&quot;)]</target>
                </targets>
                <priority>1</priority>
                <pathAliases>
                    <pathAlias name="HMS">../cell[(@column=&quot;SecondsSinceLastUpdate&quot;)]</pathAlias>
                </pathAliases>
                <block>
                    <!--Only works for values up to 86399-->
                    <set>
                        <var ref="secs"></var>
                        <dataItem>
                            <pathAlias ref="HMS"></pathAlias>
                            <property>@value</property>
                        </dataItem>
                    </set>
                    <set>
                        <var ref="X"></var>
                        <printDate>
                            <string>%H:%M:%S</string>
                            <var ref="secs"></var>
                        </printDate>
                    </set>
                    <transaction>
                        <update>
                            <property>@value</property>
                            <substr>
                                <printDate>
                                    <string>%H:%M:%S %Z</string>
                                    <var ref="secs"></var>
                                    <string>Europe/London</string>
                                </printDate>
                                <integer>1</integer>
                                <integer>8</integer>
                            </substr>
                        </update>
                    </transaction>
                    <!--value substr(printDate("%H hours %M minutes %S seconds %Z", $(secs), "Europe/London"), 1, 30)-->
                </block>
            </rule>
        </ruleGroup>
        <ruleGroup name="Luke ISIN">
            <rule name="AP_and_BP">
                <targets>
                    <target>/geneos/gateway/directory/probe/managedEntity/sampler[(@name=&quot;Luke toolkit&quot;)][(@type=&quot;&quot;)]/dataview[(@name=&quot;Luke toolkit&quot;)]/rows/row[not(wild(@name,&quot;*TIME&quot;))]/cell[(@column=&quot;ISIN&quot;)]</target>
                </targets>
                <priority>1</priority>
                <pathAliases>
                    <pathAlias name="SVR1">../cell[(@column=&quot;gbwmaptwebp200&quot;)]</pathAlias>
                    <pathAlias name="SVR2">../cell[(@column=&quot;gbwmaptwebp001&quot;)]</pathAlias>
                    <pathAlias name="SVR3">../cell[(@column=&quot;gbwmapcntxq301&quot;)]</pathAlias>
                    <pathAlias name="SVR4">../cell[(@column=&quot;MDET - gdp/lon/dev&quot;)]</pathAlias>
                </pathAliases>
                <block>
                    <set>
                        <var ref="A"></var>
                        <dataItem>
                            <pathAlias ref="SVR1"></pathAlias>
                            <property>@value</property>
                        </dataItem>
                    </set>
                    <set>
                        <var ref="B"></var>
                        <dataItem>
                            <pathAlias ref="SVR2"></pathAlias>
                            <property>@value</property>
                        </dataItem>
                    </set>
                    <set>
                        <var ref="C"></var>
                        <dataItem>
                            <pathAlias ref="SVR3"></pathAlias>
                            <property>@value</property>
                        </dataItem>
                    </set>
                    <set>
                        <var ref="D"></var>
                        <dataItem>
                            <pathAlias ref="SVR4"></pathAlias>
                            <property>@value</property>
                        </dataItem>
                    </set>
                    <set>
                        <var ref="MIN"></var>
                        <minimum>
                            <var ref="A"></var>
                            <var ref="B"></var>
                            <var ref="C"></var>
                            <var ref="D"></var>
                        </minimum>
                    </set>
                    <set>
                        <var ref="MAX"></var>
                        <maximum>
                            <var ref="A"></var>
                            <var ref="B"></var>
                            <var ref="C"></var>
                            <var ref="D"></var>
                        </maximum>
                    </set>
                    <if>
                        <notEqual>
                            <var ref="MIN"></var>
                            <var ref="MAX"></var>
                        </notEqual>
                        <transaction>
                            <update>
                                <property>state/@severity</property>
                                <severity>warning</severity>
                            </update>
                        </transaction>
                        <transaction>
                            <update>
                                <property>state/@severity</property>
                                <severity>ok</severity>
                            </update>
                        </transaction>
                    </if>
                </block>
            </rule>
            <rule name="Time">
                <targets>
                    <target>/geneos/gateway/directory/probe/managedEntity/sampler[(@name=&quot;Luke toolkit&quot;)][(@type=&quot;&quot;)]/dataview[(@name=&quot;Luke toolkit&quot;)]/rows/row[wild(@name,&quot;*TIME&quot;)]/cell[(@column=&quot;ISIN&quot;)]</target>
                </targets>
                <priority>1</priority>
                <pathAliases>
                    <pathAlias name="SVR1">../cell[(@column=&quot;gbwmaptwebp200&quot;)]</pathAlias>
                    <pathAlias name="SVR2">../cell[(@column=&quot;gbwmaptwebp001&quot;)]</pathAlias>
                    <pathAlias name="SVR3">../cell[(@column=&quot;gbwmapcntxq301&quot;)]</pathAlias>
                    <pathAlias name="SVR4">../cell[(@column=&quot;MDET - gdp/lon/dev&quot;)]</pathAlias>
                </pathAliases>
                <block>
                    <set>
                        <var ref="A"></var>
                        <parseDate>
                            <string>%H:%M:%S</string>
                            <dataItem>
                                <pathAlias ref="SVR1"></pathAlias>
                                <property>@value</property>
                            </dataItem>
                        </parseDate>
                    </set>
                    <set>
                        <var ref="B"></var>
                        <parseDate>
                            <string>%H:%M:%S</string>
                            <dataItem>
                                <pathAlias ref="SVR2"></pathAlias>
                                <property>@value</property>
                            </dataItem>
                        </parseDate>
                    </set>
                    <set>
                        <var ref="C"></var>
                        <parseDate>
                            <string>%H:%M:%S</string>
                            <dataItem>
                                <pathAlias ref="SVR3"></pathAlias>
                                <property>@value</property>
                            </dataItem>
                        </parseDate>
                    </set>
                    <set>
                        <var ref="D"></var>
                        <parseDate>
                            <string>%H:%M:%S</string>
                            <dataItem>
                                <pathAlias ref="SVR4"></pathAlias>
                                <property>@value</property>
                            </dataItem>
                        </parseDate>
                    </set>
                    <set>
                        <var ref="MIN"></var>
                        <minimum>
                            <var ref="A"></var>
                            <var ref="B"></var>
                            <var ref="C"></var>
                            <var ref="D"></var>
                        </minimum>
                    </set>
                    <set>
                        <var ref="MAX"></var>
                        <maximum>
                            <var ref="A"></var>
                            <var ref="B"></var>
                            <var ref="C"></var>
                            <var ref="D"></var>
                        </maximum>
                    </set>
                    <set>
                        <var ref="variance"></var>
                        <abs>
                            <subtract>
                                <var ref="MIN"></var>
                                <var ref="MAX"></var>
                            </subtract>
                        </abs>
                    </set>
                    <if>
                        <gt>
                            <var ref="variance"></var>
                            <integer>30</integer>
                        </gt>
                        <transaction>
                            <update>
                                <property>state/@severity</property>
                                <severity>warning</severity>
                            </update>
                        </transaction>
                        <transaction>
                            <update>
                                <property>state/@severity</property>
                                <severity>ok</severity>
                            </update>
                        </transaction>
                    </if>
                </block>
            </rule>
        </ruleGroup>
        <ruleGroup name="network">
            <rule name="network\duplex">
                <targets>
                    <target>/geneos/gateway/directory/probe/managedEntity/sampler[(@name=&quot;network&quot;)]/dataview[(@name=&quot;network&quot;)]/rows/row/cell[(@column=&quot;duplex&quot;)]</target>
                </targets>
                <priority>10000</priority>
                <pathAliases>
                    <pathAlias name="ip_address">../cell[(@column=&quot;ipAddress&quot;)]</pathAlias>
                </pathAliases>
                <block>
                    <if>
                        <equal>
                            <dataItem>
                                <property>@value</property>
                            </dataItem>
                            <string></string>
                        </equal>
                        <transaction>
                            <update>
                                <property>state/@severity</property>
                                <severity>undefined</severity>
                            </update>
                        </transaction>
                        <if>
                            <and>
                                <equal>
                                    <toUpper>
                                        <dataItem>
                                            <property>@value</property>
                                        </dataItem>
                                    </toUpper>
                                    <string>HD</string>
                                </equal>
                                <notEqual>
                                    <dataItem>
                                        <pathAlias ref="ip_address"></pathAlias>
                                        <property>@value</property>
                                    </dataItem>
                                    <string></string>
                                </notEqual>
                            </and>
                            <transaction>
                                <update>
                                    <property>state/@severity</property>
                                    <severity>warning</severity>
                                </update>
                            </transaction>
                            <transaction>
                                <update>
                                    <property>state/@severity</property>
                                    <severity>ok</severity>
                                </update>
                            </transaction>
                        </if>
                    </if>
                </block>
            </rule>
            <rule name="network\kbs_recv_average">
                <targets>
                    <target>/geneos/gateway/directory/probe/managedEntity/sampler[(@name=&quot;network&quot;)]/dataview[(@name=&quot;network&quot;)]/rows/row/cell[(@column=&quot;kbyteRecvRateAverage&quot;)]</target>
                </targets>
                <priority>9000</priority>
                <pathAliases>
                    <pathAlias name="kbyterecvrate">../cell[(@column=&quot;kbyteReceiveRate&quot;)]</pathAlias>
                </pathAliases>
                <evaluateOnDataviewSample>true</evaluateOnDataviewSample>
                <block>
                    <set>
                        <var ref="avg"></var>
                        <average>
                            <historicalDataItem>
                                <pathAlias ref="kbyterecvrate"></pathAlias>
                                <property>@value</property>
                                <historyPeriod ref="rolling_day_history_period"></historyPeriod>
                            </historicalDataItem>
                        </average>
                    </set>
                    <if>
                        <and>
                            <unlike>
                                <var ref="avg"></var>
                                <string></string>
                            </unlike>
                            <unlike>
                                <dataItem>
                                    <property>@value</property>
                                </dataItem>
                                <string></string>
                            </unlike>
                        </and>
                        <transaction>
                            <update>
                                <property>@value</property>
                                <format>
                                    <string>%.2f kbytes/sec</string>
                                    <var ref="avg"></var>
                                </format>
                            </update>
                        </transaction>
                    </if>
                    <!--if path "kbyterecvrate" value = "" then-->
                    <!--  value "0.00 kbytes/sec"-->
                    <!--else-->
                    <!--  value format("%.2f kbytes/sec", average(path "kbyterecvrate" value for "rolling_day_history_period"))-->
                    <!--endif-->
                </block>
            </rule>

            <rule name="network\link">
                <targets>
                    <target>/geneos/gateway/directory/probe/managedEntity/sampler[param(&quot;PluginName&quot;)=&quot;NETWORK&quot;]/dataview/rows/row/cell[@column=&quot;link&quot;]</target>
                </targets>
                <priority>10000</priority>
                <stopFurtherEvaluation>true</stopFurtherEvaluation>
                <block>
                    <if>
                        <equal>
                            <dataItem>
                                <property>@value</property>
                            </dataItem>
                            <string></string>
                        </equal>
                        <transaction>
                            <update>
                                <property>state/@severity</property>
                                <severity>undefined</severity>
                            </update>
                        </transaction>
                        <if>
                            <equal>
                                <toUpper>
                                    <stringBefore>
                                        <dataItem>
                                            <property>@value</property>
                                        </dataItem>
                                        <string>:</string>
                                    </stringBefore>
                                </toUpper>
                                <string>DOWN</string>
                            </equal>
                            <transaction>
                                <update>
                                    <property>state/@severity</property>
                                    <severity>critical</severity>
                                </update>
                            </transaction>
                            <transaction>
                                <update>
                                    <property>state/@severity</property>
                                    <severity>ok</severity>
                                </update>
                            </transaction>
                        </if>
                    </if>
                </block>
            </rule>

                    <target>/geneos/gateway/directory/probe/managedEntity/sampler[(@name=&quot;win-network&quot;)]/dataview[(@name=&quot;NT-NETWORK&quot;)]/rows/row/cell[(@column=&quot;packetReceiveDiscardedRate&quot;)]</target>
                    <target>/geneos/gateway/directory/probe/managedEntity/sampler[(@name=&quot;win-network&quot;)]/dataview[(@name=&quot;NT-NETWORK&quot;)]/rows/row/cell[(@column=&quot;packetSentErrorRate&quot;)]</target>
                    <target>/geneos/gateway/directory/probe/managedEntity/sampler[(@name=&quot;win-network&quot;)]/dataview[(@name=&quot;NT-NETWORK&quot;)]/rows/row/cell[(@column=&quot;packetReceiveErrorRate&quot;)]</target>
                    <target>/geneos/gateway/directory/probe/managedEntity/sampler[(@name=&quot;network&quot;)]/dataview[(@name=&quot;network&quot;)]/rows/row/cell[(@column=&quot;percentSendErrors&quot;)]</target>
                    <target>/geneos/gateway/directory/probe/managedEntity/sampler[(@name=&quot;network&quot;)]/dataview[(@name=&quot;network&quot;)]/rows/row/cell[(@column=&quot;percentRecvErrors&quot;)]</target>
                    <target>/geneos/gateway/directory/probe/managedEntity/sampler[(@name=&quot;network&quot;)]/dataview[(@name=&quot;network&quot;)]/rows/row/cell[(@column=&quot;percentFramingErrors&quot;)]</target>
                    <target>/geneos/gateway/directory/probe/managedEntity/sampler[(@name=&quot;network&quot;)]/dataview[(@name=&quot;network&quot;)]/rows/row/cell[(@column=&quot;percentCrcErrors&quot;)]</target>
                </targets>
                <priority>10000</priority>
                <stopFurtherEvaluation>true</stopFurtherEvaluation>
                <block>
                    <if>
                        <equal>
                            <dataItem>
                                <property>@value</property>
                            </dataItem>
                            <string></string>
                        </equal>
                        <transaction>
                            <update>
                                <property>state/@severity</property>
                                <severity>undefined</severity>
                            </update>
                        </transaction>
                        <if>
                            <gt>
                                <dataItem>
                                    <property>@value</property>
                                </dataItem>
                                <double>0.5</double>
                            </gt>
                            <transaction>
                                <delay>45</delay>
                                <update>
                                    <property>state/@severity</property>
                                    <severity>critical</severity>
                                </update>
                            </transaction>
                            <if>
                                <gt>
                                    <dataItem>
                                        <property>@value</property>
                                    </dataItem>
                                    <double>0.2</double>
                                </gt>
                                <transaction>
                                    <delay>45</delay>
                                    <update>
                                        <property>state/@severity</property>
                                        <severity>warning</severity>
                                    </update>
                                </transaction>
                                <transaction>
                                    <update>
                                        <property>state/@severity</property>
                                        <severity>ok</severity>
                                    </update>
                                </transaction>
                            </if>
                        </if>
                    </if>
                </block>
            </rule>

            <rule name="win_network\byterecvrate">
                <targets>
                    <target>/geneos/gateway/directory/probe/managedEntity/sampler[(@name=&quot;win-network&quot;)]/dataview[(@name=&quot;NT-NETWORK&quot;)]/rows/row/cell[(@column=&quot;kbyteRecvRate&quot;)]</target>
                </targets>
                <priority>10000</priority>
                <pathAliases>
                    <pathAlias name="byteRecvRate">../cell[(@column=&quot;byteReceiveRate&quot;)]</pathAlias>
                </pathAliases>
                <evaluateOnDataviewSample>true</evaluateOnDataviewSample>
                <block>
                    <set>
                        <var ref="brr"></var>
                        <dataItem>
                            <pathAlias ref="byteRecvRate"></pathAlias>
                            <property>@value</property>
                        </dataItem>
                    </set>
                    <transaction>
                        <update>
                            <property>@value</property>
                            <format>
                                <string>%.2f kbyte/sec</string>
                                <divide>
                                    <var ref="brr"></var>
                                    <integer>1024</integer>
                                </divide>
                            </format>
                        </update>
                    </transaction>
                </block>
            </rule>

            <rule name="win_network\kbs_recv_average">
                <targets>
                    <target>/geneos/gateway/directory/probe/managedEntity/sampler[(@name=&quot;win-network&quot;)]/dataview[(@name=&quot;NT-NETWORK&quot;)]/rows/row/cell[(@column=&quot;kbyteRecvRateAverage&quot;)]</target>
                </targets>
                <priority>9000</priority>
                <pathAliases>
                    <pathAlias name="kbyterecvrate">../cell[(@column=&quot;kbyteRecvRate&quot;)]</pathAlias>
                </pathAliases>
                <evaluateOnDataviewSample>true</evaluateOnDataviewSample>
                <block>
                    <set>
                        <var ref="avg"></var>
                        <average>
                            <historicalDataItem>
                                <pathAlias ref="kbyterecvrate"></pathAlias>
                                <property>@value</property>
                                <historyPeriod ref="rolling_day_history_period"></historyPeriod>
                            </historicalDataItem>
                        </average>
                    </set>
                    <if>
                        <and>
                            <unlike>
                                <var ref="avg"></var>
                                <string></string>
                            </unlike>
                            <unlike>
                                <dataItem>
                                    <property>@value</property>
                                </dataItem>
                                <string></string>
                            </unlike>
                        </and>
                        <transaction>
                            <update>
                                <property>@value</property>
                                <format>
                                    <string>%.2f kbytes/sec</string>
                                    <var ref="avg"></var>
                                </format>
                            </update>
                        </transaction>
                    </if>
                    <!--if path "kbyterecvrate" value = "" then-->
                    <!--  value "0.00 kbytes/sec"-->
                    <!--else-->
                    <!--  value format("%.2f kbytes/sec", average(path "kbyterecvrate" value for "rolling_day_history_period"))-->
                    <!--endif-->
                </block>
            </rule>

            <rule name="Count of ambers">
                <targets>
                    <target>/geneos/gateway[(@name=&quot;TheOneAndOnlyGW2_RJB  port 9876&quot;)]/directory/probe[(@name=&quot;srv01_port_60013&quot;)]/managedEntity[(@name=&quot;SRV01_RMS_upgrade_test&quot;)]/sampler[(@name=&quot;C&quot;)][(@type=&quot;&quot;)]/dataview[(@name=&quot;C&quot;)]/headlines/cell[(@name=&quot;NumberAmber&quot;)]</target>
                </targets>
                <priority>1</priority>
                <pathAliases>
                    <pathAlias name="WorstCase">../../rows/row/cell[(state(&quot;severity&quot;)=&quot;2&quot;)][(@column=&quot;%privilegedTime&quot;)]</pathAlias>
                </pathAliases>
                <evaluateOnDataviewSample>true</evaluateOnDataviewSample>
                <block>
                    <transaction>
                        <update>
                            <property>@value</property>
                            <count>
                                <dataItems>
                                    <pathAlias ref="WorstCase"></pathAlias>
                                    <property>@value</property>
                                </dataItems>
                            </count>
                        </update>
                    </transaction>
                    <if>
                        <gt>
                            <dataItem>
                                <property>@value</property>
                            </dataItem>
                            <integer>0</integer>
                        </gt>
                        <transaction>
                            <update>
                                <property>state/@severity</property>
                                <severity>warning</severity>
                            </update>
                        </transaction>
                        <transaction>
                            <update>
                                <property>state/@severity</property>
                                <severity>undefined</severity>
                            </update>
                        </transaction>
                    </if>
                </block>
            </rule>

            <rule name="cpq_health\status">
                <targets>
                    <target>/geneos/gateway/directory/probe/managedEntity/sampler/dataview[@name=&quot;cpq_health&quot;]/rows/row/cell[@column=&quot;status&quot;]</target>
                </targets>
                <priority>10000</priority>
                <stopFurtherEvaluation>true</stopFurtherEvaluation>
                <block>
                    <if>
                        <equal>
                            <dataItem>
                                <property>@value</property>
                            </dataItem>
                            <string></string>
                        </equal>
                        <transaction>
                            <update>
                                <property>state/@severity</property>
                                <severity>undefined</severity>
                            </update>
                        </transaction>
                        <if>
                            <equal>
                                <dataItem>
                                    <property>@value</property>
                                </dataItem>
                                <string>OK</string>
                            </equal>
                            <transaction>
                                <update>
                                    <property>state/@severity</property>
                                    <severity>ok</severity>
                                </update>
                            </transaction>
                            <if>
                                <equal>
                                    <toUpper>
                                        <dataItem>
                                            <property>@value</property>
                                        </dataItem>
                                    </toUpper>
                                    <string>NOMINAL</string>
                                </equal>
                                <transaction>
                                    <update>
                                        <property>state/@severity</property>
                                        <severity>ok</severity>
                                    </update>
                                </transaction>
                                <transaction>
                                    <update>
                                        <property>state/@severity</property>
                                        <severity>critical</severity>
                                    </update>
                                </transaction>
                            </if>
                        </if>
                    </if>
                </block>
            </rule>
            <rule name="cpu\cpu_state">
                <targets>
                    <target>/geneos/gateway/directory/probe/managedEntity/sampler[param(&quot;PluginName&quot;)=&quot;CPU&quot;]/dataview/rows/row[wild(@name,&quot;cpu*&quot;)]/cell[@column=&quot;state&quot;]</target>
                </targets>
                <priority>9000</priority>
                <stopFurtherEvaluation>true</stopFurtherEvaluation>
                <block>
                    <if>
                        <equal>
                            <dataItem>
                                <property>@value</property>
                            </dataItem>
                            <string></string>
                        </equal>
                        <transaction>
                            <update>
                                <property>state/@severity</property>
                                <severity>undefined</severity>
                            </update>
                        </transaction>
                        <if>
                            <equal>
                                <toUpper>
                                    <stringBefore>
                                        <dataItem>
                                            <property>@value</property>
                                        </dataItem>
                                        <string>:</string>
                                    </stringBefore>
                                </toUpper>
                                <string>ON-LINE</string>
                            </equal>
                            <transaction>
                                <update>
                                    <property>state/@severity</property>
                                    <severity>ok</severity>
                                </update>
                            </transaction>
                            <if>
                                <equal>
                                    <toUpper>
                                        <stringBefore>
                                            <dataItem>
                                                <property>@value</property>
                                            </dataItem>
                                            <string>:</string>
                                        </stringBefore>
                                    </toUpper>
                                    <string>NO-INTR</string>
                                </equal>
                                <transaction>
                                    <update>
                                        <property>state/@severity</property>
                                        <severity>ok</severity>
                                    </update>
                                </transaction>
                                <transaction>
                                    <update>
                                        <property>state/@severity</property>
                                        <severity>critical</severity>
                                    </update>
                                </transaction>
                            </if>
                        </if>
                    </if>
                </block>
            </rule>

                                <integer>100</integer>
                            </equal>
                            <transaction>

                                <update>
                                    <property>state/@severity</property>
                                    <severity>critical</severity>
                                </update>
                            </transaction>
                            <if>
                                <gt>
                                    <dataItem>
                                        <property>@value</property>
                                    </dataItem>
                                    <integer>85</integer>
                                </gt>
                                <transaction>
                                    <delay unit="samples">8</delay>
                                    <update>
                                        <property>state/@severity</property>
                                        <severity>warning</severity>
                                    </update>
                                </transaction>
                                <transaction>
                                    <update>
                                        <property>state/@severity</property>
                                        <severity>ok</severity>
                                    </update>
                                </transaction>
                            </if>
                        </if>
                    </if>
                </block>

                                    </stringBefore>
                                </toUpper>

                            </equal>

                                    <property>state/@severity</property>
                                    <severity>warning</severity>
                                </update>
