            <rule name="processes\percent_cpu_average">
                <targets>
                    <target>/geneos/gateway/directory/probe/managedEntity/sampler/dataview[(@name=&quot;P&quot;)]/rows/row/cell[(@column=&quot;percentCPUAverage&quot;)]</target>
                    <target>/geneos/gateway/directory/probe/managedEntity/sampler[(@name=&quot;sles-processes&quot;)]/dataview[(@name=&quot;sles-processes&quot;)]/rows/row/cell[(@column=&quot;percentCPUAverage&quot;)]</target>
                </targets>
                <priority>9000</priority>
                <stopFurtherEvaluation>true</stopFurtherEvaluation>
                <pathAliases>
                    <pathAlias name="percent_cpu">../cell[(@column=&quot;percentCPU&quot;)]</pathAlias>
                </pathAliases>
                <evaluateOnDataviewSample>true</evaluateOnDataviewSample>
                <block>
                    <set>
                        <var ref="avg"></var>
                        <average>
                            <historicalDataItem>
                                <pathAlias ref="percent_cpu"></pathAlias>
                                <property>@value</property>
                                <historyPeriod ref="rolling_hour_history_period"></historyPeriod>
                            </historicalDataItem>
                        </average>
                    </set>
                    <if>
                        <and>
                            <unlike>
                                <var ref="avg"></var>
                                <string></string>
                            </unlike>
                            <unlike>
                                <dataItem>
                                    <property>@value</property>
                                </dataItem>
                                <string></string>
                            </unlike>
                        </and>
                        <transaction>
                            <update>
                                <property>@value</property>
                                <format>
                                    <string>%.2f %%</string>
                                    <var ref="avg"></var>
                                </format>
                            </update>
                        </transaction>
                    </if>
                    <!--if path "percent_cpu" value = "" then-->
                    <!--  value "0.00 %"-->
                    <!--else-->
                    <!--  value format("%.2f %%", average(path "percent_cpu" value for "rolling_hour_history_period"))-->
                    <!--endif-->
                </block>
            </rule>
            <rule name="processes\percent_cpu_max">

            <rule name="scripterror">
                <targets>
                    <target>/geneos/gateway/directory/probe/managedEntity/sampler/dataview/headlines/cell[@name=&quot;ScriptError&quot;]</target>
                </targets>
                <priority>9000</priority>
                <stopFurtherEvaluation>true</stopFurtherEvaluation>
                <block>
                    <if>
                        <notEqual>
                            <toUpper>
                                <dataItem>
                                    <property>@value</property>
                                </dataItem>
                            </toUpper>
                            <string></string>
                        </notEqual>
                        <transaction>
                            <update>
                                <property>state/@severity</property>
                                <severity>warning</severity>
                            </update>
                        </transaction>
                        <transaction>
                            <update>
                                <property>state/@severity</property>
                                <severity>ok</severity>
                            </update>
                        </transaction>
                    </if>
                </block>
            </rule>
            <rule name="temperature\temperature">
                <targets>
                    <target>/geneos/gateway/directory/probe/managedEntity/sampler/dataview[@name=&quot;temperature&quot;]/rows/row/cell[@column=&quot;temperature&quot;]</target>
                </targets>
                <priority>10000</priority>
                <stopFurtherEvaluation>true</stopFurtherEvaluation>
                <block>
                    <if>
                        <equal>
                            <dataItem>
                                <property>@value</property>
                            </dataItem>
                            <string></string>
                        </equal>
                        <transaction>
                            <update>
                                <property>state/@severity</property>
                                <severity>undefined</severity>
                            </update>
                        </transaction>
                        <if>
                            <gt>
                                <dataItem>
                                    <property>@value</property>
                                </dataItem>
                                <integer>90</integer>
                            </gt>
                            <transaction>
                                <update>
                                    <property>state/@severity</property>
                                    <severity>critical</severity>
                                </update>
                            </transaction>
                            <if>
                                <gt>
                                    <dataItem>
                                        <property>@value</property>
                                    </dataItem>
                                    <integer>80</integer>
                                </gt>
                                <transaction>
                                    <update>
                                        <property>state/@severity</property>
                                        <severity>warning</severity>
                                    </update>
                                </transaction>
                                <transaction>
                                    <update>
                                        <property>state/@severity</property>
                                        <severity>ok</severity>
                                    </update>
                                </transaction>
                            </if>
                        </if>
                    </if>
                </block>
            </rule>
            <rule name="wmi\state">
                <targets>
                    <target>/geneos/gateway/directory/probe/managedEntity/sampler[(@name=&quot;win-processes&quot;)][(@type=&quot;windows&quot;)]/dataview[(@name=&quot;win-processes&quot;)]/rows/row[(@name=&quot;WMI&quot;)]/cell[(@column=&quot;instanceCount&quot;)]</target>
                </targets>
                <priority>5000</priority>
                <block>
                    <if>
                        <equal>
                            <dataItem>

                            </dataItem>
                            <integer>0</integer>
                        </equal>
                        <transaction>
                            <update>
                                <property>state/@severity</property>
                                <severity>critical</severity>
                            </update>
                            <action ref="restart_win_netprobe"></action>
                        </transaction>
                        <transaction>
                            <update>
                                <property>state/@severity</property>
                                <severity>ok</severity>
                            </update>
                        </transaction>
                    </if>
                </block>
            </rule>

            <ruleGroup name="network">
                <rule name="network\duplex">
                    <targets>
                        <target>/geneos/gateway/directory/probe/managedEntity/sampler[(@name=&quot;network&quot;)]/dataview[(@name=&quot;network&quot;)]/rows/row/cell[(@column=&quot;duplex&quot;)]</target>
                    </targets>
                    <priority>10000</priority>
                    <pathAliases>
                        <pathAlias name="ip_address">../cell[(@column=&quot;ipAddress&quot;)]</pathAlias>
                    </pathAliases>
                    <block>
                        <if>
                            <equal>
                                <dataItem>
                                    <property>@value</property>
                                </dataItem>
                                <string></string>
                            </equal>
                            <transaction>
                                <update>
                                    <property>state/@severity</property>
                                    <severity>undefined</severity>
                                </update>
                            </transaction>
                            <if>
                                <and>
                                    <equal>
                                        <toUpper>
                                            <dataItem>
                                                <property>@value</property>
                                            </dataItem>
                                        </toUpper>
                                        <string>HD</string>
                                    </equal>
                                    <notEqual>
                                        <dataItem>
                                            <pathAlias ref="ip_address"></pathAlias>
                                            <property>@value</property>
                                        </dataItem>
                                        <string></string>
                                    </notEqual>
                                </and>
                                <transaction>
                                    <update>
                                        <property>state/@severity</property>
                                        <severity>warning</severity>
                                    </update>
                                </transaction>
                                <transaction>
                                    <update>
                                        <property>state/@severity</property>
                                        <severity>ok</severity>
                                    </update>
                                </transaction>
                            </if>
                        </if>
                    </block>
                </rule>
                <rule name="network\kbs_recv_average">
                    <targets>
                        <target>/geneos/gateway/directory/probe/managedEntity/sampler[(@name=&quot;network&quot;)]/dataview[(@name=&quot;network&quot;)]/rows/row/cell[(@column=&quot;kbyteRecvRateAverage&quot;)]</target>
                    </targets>
                    <priority>9000</priority>
                    <pathAliases>
                        <pathAlias name="kbyterecvrate">../cell[(@column=&quot;kbyteReceiveRate&quot;)]</pathAlias>
                    </pathAliases>
                    <evaluateOnDataviewSample>true</evaluateOnDataviewSample>
                    <block>
                        <set>
                            <var ref="avg"></var>
                            <average>
                                <historicalDataItem>
                                    <pathAlias ref="kbyterecvrate"></pathAlias>
                                    <property>@value</property>
                                    <historyPeriod ref="rolling_day_history_period"></historyPeriod>
                                </historicalDataItem>
                            </average>
                        </set>
                        <if>
                            <and>
                                <unlike>
                                    <var ref="avg"></var>
                                    <string></string>
                                </unlike>
                                <unlike>
                                    <dataItem>
                                        <property>@value</property>
                                    </dataItem>
                                    <string></string>
                                </unlike>
                            </and>
                            <transaction>
                                <update>
                                    <property>@value</property>
                                    <format>
                                        <string>%.2f kbytes/sec</string>
                                        <var ref="avg"></var>
                                    </format>
                                </update>
                            </transaction>
                        </if>
                        <!--if path "kbyterecvrate" value = "" then-->
                        <!--  value "0.00 kbytes/sec"-->
                        <!--else-->
                        <!--  value format("%.2f kbytes/sec", average(path "kbyterecvrate" value for "rolling_day_history_period"))-->
                        <!--endif-->
                    </block>
                </rule>
                <rule name="network\kbs_recv_max">
                    <targets>
                        <target>/geneos/gateway/directory/probe/managedEntity/sampler[(@name=&quot;network&quot;)]/dataview[(@name=&quot;network&quot;)]/rows/row/cell[(@column=&quot;kbyteRecvRateMax&quot;)]</target>
                    </targets>
                    <priority>9000</priority>
                    <pathAliases>
                        <pathAlias name="kbyterecvrate">../cell[(@column=&quot;kbyteReceiveRate&quot;)]</pathAlias>
                    </pathAliases>
                    <evaluateOnDataviewSample>true</evaluateOnDataviewSample>
                    <block>
                        <set>
                            <var ref="max"></var>
                            <maximum>
                                <historicalDataItem>
                                    <pathAlias ref="kbyterecvrate"></pathAlias>
                                    <property>@value</property>
                                    <historyPeriod ref="rolling_day_history_period"></historyPeriod>
                                </historicalDataItem>
                            </maximum>
                        </set>
                        <if>
                            <and>
                                <unlike>
                                    <var ref="max"></var>
                                    <string></string>
                                </unlike>
                                <unlike>
                                    <dataItem>
                                        <property>@value</property>
                                    </dataItem>
                                    <string></string>
                                </unlike>
                            </and>
                            <transaction>
                                <update>
                                    <property>@value</property>
                                    <format>
                                        <string>%.2f kbytes/sec</string>
                                        <var ref="max"></var>
                                    </format>
                                </update>
                            </transaction>
                        </if>
                        <!--if path "kbyterecvrate" value = "" then-->
                        <!--  value "0.00 kbytes/sec"-->
                        <!--else-->
                        <!--  value format("%.2f kbytes/sec", maximum(path "kbyterecvrate" value for "rolling_day_history_period"))-->
                        <!--endif-->
                    </block>
                </rule>
                <rule name="network\kbs_send_average">
                    <targets>
                        <target>/geneos/gateway/directory/probe/managedEntity/sampler[(@name=&quot;network&quot;)]/dataview[(@name=&quot;network&quot;)]/rows/row/cell[(@column=&quot;kbyteSendRateAverage&quot;)]</target>
                    </targets>
                    <priority>9000</priority>
                    <pathAliases>
                        <pathAlias name="kbytesendrate">../cell[(@column=&quot;kbyteSendRate&quot;)]</pathAlias>
                    </pathAliases>
                    <evaluateOnDataviewSample>true</evaluateOnDataviewSample>
                    <block>
                        <set>
                            <var ref="avg"></var>
                            <average>
                                <historicalDataItem>
                                    <pathAlias ref="kbytesendrate"></pathAlias>
                                    <property>@value</property>
                                    <historyPeriod ref="rolling_day_history_period"></historyPeriod>
                                </historicalDataItem>
                            </average>
                        </set>
                        <if>
                            <and>
                                <unlike>
                                    <var ref="avg"></var>
                                    <string></string>
                                </unlike>
                                <unlike>
                                    <dataItem>
                                        <property>@value</property>
                                    </dataItem>
                                    <string></string>
                                </unlike>
                            </and>
                            <transaction>
                                <update>
                                    <property>@value</property>
                                    <format>
                                        <string>%.2f kbytes/sec</string>
                                        <var ref="avg"></var>
                                    </format>
                                </update>
                            </transaction>
                        </if>
                        <!--if path "kbytesendrate" value = "" then-->
                        <!--  value "0.00 kbytes/sec"-->
                        <!--else-->
                        <!--  value format("%.2f kbytes/sec", average(path "kbytesendrate" value for "rolling_day_history_period"))-->
                        <!--endif-->
                    </block>
                </rule>

                <rule name="network\link">
                    <targets>
                        <target>/geneos/gateway/directory/probe/managedEntity/sampler[param(&quot;PluginName&quot;)=&quot;NETWORK&quot;]/dataview/rows/row/cell[@column=&quot;link&quot;]</target>
                    </targets>
                    <priority>10000</priority>
                    <stopFurtherEvaluation>true</stopFurtherEvaluation>
                    <block>
                        <if>
                            <equal>
                                <dataItem>
                                    <property>@value</property>
                                </dataItem>
                                <string></string>
                            </equal>
                            <transaction>
                                <update>
                                    <property>state/@severity</property>
                                    <severity>undefined</severity>
                                </update>
                            </transaction>
                            <if>
                                <equal>
                                    <toUpper>
                                        <stringBefore>
                                            <dataItem>
                                                <property>@value</property>
                                            </dataItem>
                                            <string>:</string>
                                        </stringBefore>
                                    </toUpper>
                                    <string>DOWN</string>
                                </equal>
                                <transaction>
                                    <update>
                                        <property>state/@severity</property>
                                        <severity>critical</severity>
                                    </update>
                                </transaction>
                                <transaction>
                                    <update>
                                        <property>state/@severity</property>
                                        <severity>ok</severity>
                                    </update>
                                </transaction>
                            </if>
                        </if>
                    </block>
                </rule>

                            </equal>

                                    <property>state/@severity</property>
                                    <severity>undefined</severity>
                                </update>
                            </transaction>
                            <if>
                                <gt>
                                    <dataItem>
                                        <property>@value</property>
                                    </dataItem>
                                    <double>0.5</double>
                                </gt>
                                <transaction>
                                    <delay>45</delay>
                                    <update>
                                        <property>state/@severity</property>
                                        <severity>critical</severity>
                                    </update>
                                </transaction>
                                <if>
                                    <gt>
                                        <dataItem>
                                            <property>@value</property>
                                        </dataItem>
                                        <double>0.2</double>
                                    </gt>

                                        <delay>45</delay>

                                    </transaction>

            <rule name="Add last sample time to headline cell">
                <targets>
                    <target>/geneos/gateway[(@name=&quot;TheOneAndOnlyGW2_RJB  port 9886&quot;)]/directory/probe[(@name=&quot;RJBVM_32&quot;)]/managedEntity[(@name=&quot;WORLD CLOCK&quot;)]/sampler[(@name=&quot;C&quot;)][(@type=&quot;&quot;)]/dataview[(@name=&quot;C&quot;)]/headlines/cell[(@name=&quot;LastSampled&quot;)]</target>
                </targets>
                <priority>1</priority>
                <pathAliases>
                    <pathAlias name="DV">ancestor::dataview</pathAlias>
                </pathAliases>
                <block>
                    <transaction>
                        <update>
                            <property>@value</property>
                            <format>
                                <string>%.f</string>
                                <dataItem>
                                    <pathAlias ref="DV"></pathAlias>
                                    <property>runtimeParameters/@SampleTimestamp</property>
                                </dataItem>
                            </format>
                        </update>
                    </transaction>
                    <transaction>
                        <update>
                            <property>@value</property>
                            <dataItem>
                                <pathAlias ref="DV"></pathAlias>
                                <property>runtimeParameters/@SampleTime</property>
                            </dataItem>
                        </update>
                    </transaction>
                </block>
            </rule>

                </targets>
                <priority>30</priority>
                <pathAliases>
                    <pathAlias name="PU">../cell[(@column=&quot;percentUtilisation&quot;)]</pathAlias>
                    <pathAlias name="PV">../cell[(@column=&quot;PreviousValue&quot;)]</pathAlias>
                </pathAliases>
                <evaluateOnDataviewSample>true</evaluateOnDataviewSample>
                <block>
                    <set>
                        <var ref="X"></var>
                        <dataItem>
                            <pathAlias ref="PV"></pathAlias>
                            <property>@value</property>
                        </dataItem>
                    </set>
                    <set>
                        <var ref="Y"></var>
                        <dataItem>
                            <pathAlias ref="PU"></pathAlias>
                            <property>@value</property>
                        </dataItem>
                    </set>
                    <transaction>
                        <update>
                            <property>@value</property>
                            <subtract>
                                <var ref="X"></var>
                                <var ref="Y"></var>
                            </subtract>
                        </update>
                    </transaction>
                </block>
            </rule>
